      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WEFFALEE LEE LEE (1) flew the lids from the middle with a slick turn of foot before finishing second (29.82) and beaten a neck over 520m at Wentworth Park. Makes plenty of appeal. MODEST MAN (3) goes very well this course and distance starting 13 times for five wins and six minors. Hit the frame latest (25.45) when third at Grafton in a Grade 4/5. Looks suited here and can measure up. ALI TANGO (7) has a strong record this trip with 16 wins and 10 placings from 46 starts. Missed the frame latest (30.69) when sixth over 520m at Wentworth Park in a NG. Looks one of the chances. STAR (8) is in form and worth thought again.",
